ClassDesc: Callback interface for when the map is ready to be used. Once an instance of this interface is set on a @B_com#google#android#gms#maps#MapFragment_E@ or @B_com#google#android#gms#maps#MapView_E@ object, the @B_com#google#android#gms#maps#OnMapReadyCallback#onMapReady_E@ method is triggered when the map is ready to be used and provides a non-null instance of @B_com#google#android#gms#maps#GoogleMap_E@. If Google Play services is not installed on the device, the user will be prompted to install it, and the @B_com#google#android#gms#maps#OnMapReadyCallback#onMapReady_E@ method will only be triggered when the user has installed it and returned to the app.
